Request Syntax in the AWS Step Functions API Reference.If you don't want to include the ARN of your state machine in the body of your API Gateway call, you can configure a body-mapping template, as shown in the following example.{ "input": "$util.escapeJavaScript($input.json('$'))", "stateMachineArn": "arn:aws:states:us-east-1:123456789012:stateMachine:HelloWorld"
